# my keybindings
# Example keybinding to get the weather (pop-up notification)
# Real functionality requires this is set to launch a weather utility with local parameters (location, and such).
# This is a static message for testing Notifications only!!
bindsym $mod+w exec notify-send "Weather" "📍 <City, State|| Place> | 58°F | Wind: NW 2 mph | Humidity: 92% | 🧥 Jacket recommended (below 65°F)"
